RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select module_id, module_desc FROM (select module_id, module_desc from smtb_modules UNION select 'SM', 'Security Maintenance - Branch' from dual UNION select 'OT', 'Teller - Branch' from dual UNION select 'OP', 'Operations - Branch' from dual)
select lang_code from smtbs_language WHERE ONCE_AUTH ='Y' AND RECORD_STAT='O'
select b.function_id,b.executable_name from smtb_function_description a, smtb_menu b where a.Lang_Code = global.lang and a.function_id = b.function_id order by function_id
